<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="KC9">
<l>mikka vētiyar vētattiṉuṭporuḷ</l>
<l>niṟkap pāṭi yeṉ neñcuḷ niṟuttiṉāṉ</l>
<l>takka cīrc caṭakōpaṉeṉ nampik</l>
<l>kāṭpukka kātalaṭimaip payaṉaṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He [Nammalvar] sang [and] established in my heart</l>
<l>the inner meaning of the Vedas of the great Brahmins so that it remains.</l>
<l>The love that entered [this] servant of my Lord,</l>
<l>Caṭakōpaṉ of suitable excellence, is the fruit of my servitude, isn’t it?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
